      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CITY OF LOVE (2) was a course and distance placegetter (30.82) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 5.5 lengths third in a Grade 6. Has good speed and aided by a low draw. Can find winning form here. BIG BOSS GIBLET (7) racing well without winning, placing at his last six runs. Last time finished 2nd over 530m at this track beaten 4 lengths (30.72) behind Just A Babe in a Grade 6 on February 19. Must be included in calculations. VICTA HOWARD (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.96) in a Grade 6 at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Can figure in the finish. CAWBOURNE ADELE (4) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around.",
